name: Sailor Foot First...
description: These customised pumps are perfect for just chucking on and getting on the go! Comfortable and versatile they go with anything, and the pretty little buttons make them very much more unique than any ‘daps’ you would fine on the high street!! This pair is a small 5, a nice snug fit that put a spring in your step with a lovely cushioned sole!! ENJOY!! xx

name: Loch Ness Love Hearts
description: Once again another pair of comfortable pumps with customised buttons to and a bit of jazz to your feet!! This pair has been made pretty with tartan hearts and cute flowers and will fit and dainty size 4 foot! Wil once again put a bounce in your day with deliciously cushioned soles! SMILE!! xx
